# Supabase
# - For local dev: get values from `npx supabase status` after `npx supabase start`
#   (the local anon key is the classic JWT format: `eyJ...`).
# - For cloud: Settings > API. Use the publishable key (`sb_publishable_...`)
#   or the legacy JWT anon key — both are accepted by @supabase/supabase-js.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-or-publishable-key-here
